                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span><strong>Sustainable:</strong> Part of regular routine, not occasional indulgence</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
