              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <AlertCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-red-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span><strong>Temporary relief only:</strong> Feel worse after (guilt, shame, physical effects)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <AlertCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-red-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span><strong>Avoids problems:</strong> Numbs feelings instead of processing them</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <AlertCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-red-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span><strong>Creates new problems:</strong> Neglects responsibilities, damages health/relationships</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <AlertCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-red-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span><strong>Feels compulsive:</strong> Hard to stop, need more for same effect</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <AlertCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-red-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span><strong>Examples:</strong> Excessive drinking, binge eating, shopping sprees, hours of mindless scrolling</span>
